text: The 1992 Missouri Valley Conference men's soccer season was the 2nd season of men's varsity soccer in the conference. The 1992 Missouri Valley Conference Men's Soccer Tournament was hosted and won by Creighton. == Teams == == MVC Tournament == == See also == * Missouri Valley Conference * Missouri Valley Conference men's soccer tournament * 1992 NCAA Division I men's soccer season * 1992 in American soccer == References == Category:Missouri Valley Conference Category:1992 NCAA Division I men's soccer season
